              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  The detector consists of  a central cylindrical",
                " heavy-water  and  graphite  moderator  core  which is",
                " surrounded  by  48  large  BF3  proportional  neutron",
                " counters,  and located within  a paraffin  housing of",
                " 1.2 m side-length."
              ]
